### Rejestracja (To już mamy)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "marek@homie.pl",
  "password": "haslo123",
  "name": "Marek"
}

### LOGOWANIE (Testujemy to!)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "marek@homie.pl",
  "password": "haslo123"
}

